<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
      body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #1f2937; background: #f9fafb; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
      .header { background: #0A3966; padding: 32px 40px; }
      .header h1 { color: #ffffff; font-size: 22px; margin: 0; font-weight: 700; }
      .header p { color: #93c5fd; font-size: 14px; margin: 4px 0 0; }
      .body { padding: 40px; }
      .body p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151; margin: 0 0 16px; }
      .invoice-box { background: #f0f7ff; border: 1px solid #bfdbfe; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px 24px; margin: 24px 0; }
      .invoice-box .label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
      .invoice-box .value { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #0A3966; margin-top: 2px; }
      .invoice-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 12px; }
      .invoice-row .item { flex: 1; }
      .footer { padding: 24px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; background: #f9fafb; }
      .footer p { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="header">
        <h1><%= @organization.name %></h1>
        <p>Facture en pièce jointe</p>
      </div>

      <div class="body">
        <p>Bonjour <%= @client.name %>,</p>

        <p>Veuillez trouver ci-joint votre facture <strong><%= @invoice.number %></strong>.</p>

        <div class="invoice-box">
          <div class="invoice-row">
            <div class="item">
              <div class="label">Facture n°</div>
              <div class="value"><%= @invoice.number %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <div class="label">Montant TTC</div>
              <div class="value"><%= number_to_currency(@invoice.total_cents / 100.0, unit: "€", format: "%n %u") %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <div class="label">Date d'échéance</div>
              <div class="value"><%= l(@invoice.due_date, format: :long) %></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p>Pour toute question, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter à <a href="mailto:<%= @organization.email %>"><%= @organization.email %></a>.</p>

        <p>Cordialement,<br><strong><%= @organization.name %></strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Ce message a été envoyé via Facturini. La facture est disponible en pièce jointe au format PDF.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
